            elements, incorrect thermostat settings, or gas supply issues.
          </p>
        </li><li>
          <p>
            <strong>Dryer Not Tumbling:</strong> This can be caused by worn belts,
            faulty motors, or drum support problems.
          </p>
        </li><li>
          <p>
            <strong>Dryer Experiencing Airflow Issues:</strong> Typically results
            from clogged lint filters, blocked ventilation, or malfunctioning fans.
          </p>
        </li><li>
